Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Kaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been waiting for you to say that\Nall this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take back the Land of Wano,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.71,0:02:29.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden and the Akazaya members \Nchallenged Orochi and Kaido!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ashura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oden and the others got caught\Nand were sentenced to death by boiling.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's time for the execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the pot already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get in the pot at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set whatever time limit you like\Nand if any of us survive that long...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set us free!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Boiled to Death!\NOden's One-hour Struggle!"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll kill you instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going nuts, Oden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a sore loser!\NHe's so pathetic even in his final moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, bring me a watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! H-Hey! Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a big moment for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll watch it to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to survive!\NThat long in even a normal bath would be dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't go back on your word?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must follow our lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in the other world, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay on the plank, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do, Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like living in disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must switch places, Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hold you up instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and stay there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is our duty to protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my order!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His damn retainers aren't in the oil!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All 10 of them are certainly in the pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fair enough, Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NIt hasn't been even a minute yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can his skin endure it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I am going to die\Njust from this heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you whine like a loser one more time,\NI'll beat you up, Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just sitting up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, cat! It makes it harder to hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it wouldn't take long...\NThis is so boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought they'd scream more\Nand die in an entertaining manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy!\NI've had enough of the silly lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you call a silly lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say it one more time,\NI'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! She has a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}kunoichi{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, that's Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she running amok?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you insult Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you all who are the silly ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think worked hard,\Nso you can live in peace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose Oden-{\i1}sama{\i}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will realize!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly how much suffering was prevented!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi is not the Shogun or a dictator!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming a leader wasn't his purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! To me,\Nevery single person in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a sinner who mistreated \Nthe Kurozumi Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if they all die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became the Shogun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to destroy this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to get my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hate the country so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My damn grandfather\Naspired to become the Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was before you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed the Daimyo of each region one by one\Nand was sentenced to seppuku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clan fell from grace!\NAll of that was tolerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem came after that!\NThe nightmare began for the Kurozumi Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The surviving family members were hunted\Nby unknown "heroes of justice"!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Punched!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thrown into the river!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And killed!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I couldn't sleep\Nbecause I was terrified of those idiots!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even after the one who committed the crime\Nwas long dead!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurozumi! Pay for your crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're from the Daimyo-slaying family!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like even a child would be found guilty\Nif they were a Kurozumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everyone in the Land of Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...deserves my retribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you fools asked for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi! What are you gonna do with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the other room, there \Nwas a pile of weapons...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and hundreds of people \Nwho had been kidnapped!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they were handed over...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their human lives were over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tributes for Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be sold or toyed with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the cause of all of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the Land of Wano back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kozuki Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the biggest fool in the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi! Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oden-{\i}sama{\i1} got angry!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.11,0:18:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that was when Orochi made an offer!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna stop the kidnappings, Oden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you got in a war against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd lose so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what are you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:19:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just choose already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A war?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the citizens' lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't stay in this country forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've fulfilled your \Nend of the bargain...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll leave here in five years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really mean it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the silliest lord in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.44,0:21:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just a man seeking vengeance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and had no interest in the \Ncountry from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's obvious\Nthat the country would be devastated even if we won.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Oden-{\i1}sama{\i} accepted the offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he dances naked to express his apology
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Kurozumi Clan\Nevery week at the appointed time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though he would lose everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he could save 100 lives with each dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.13,0:22:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said when the ship they \Nwere building was complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.83,0:22:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'd leave the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he believed their words!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, he traveled to each region
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every week to make sure nothing went wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i} had...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden-{\i1}sama{\i} had always been\Nprotecting this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who's the silly lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Opening up the Land of Wano!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believing that the sun will rise,\NKozuki Oden burns with his fighting spirit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.71,0:23:28.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While the irritated Orochi \Nmakes the whole capital scream,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:31.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,will Oden be able to perform a miracle?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This legendary hour holds the fate of the future!\NHow will it end?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"Oden Wouldn't Be Oden If It Wasn't Boiled!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
